Real imports of goods and services

IMPGSC1 Real imports of goods and services

data(IMPGSC1)

Format

An xts object of Real imports of goods and services.

  • Release: Gross Domestic Product

  • Seasonal Adjustment: Seasonally Adjusted Annual Rate

  • Frequency: Quarterly

  • Units: Billions of Chained 2009 Dollars

  • Date Range: 1947-01-01 to 2017-07-01

  • Last Updated 2017-12-21 7:51 AM CST

Source

U.S. Bureau of Economic Analysis https://fred.stlouisfed.org/data/IMPGSC1.txt

Notes

BEA Account Code: A021RX

A Guide to the National Income and Product Accounts of the United States (NIPA) - (http://www.bea.gov/national/pdf/nipaguid.pdf)

Examples

data(IMPGSC1)
tail(IMPGSC1)
#>             [,1]
#> 2016 Q2 2684.905
#> 2016 Q3 2702.569
#> 2016 Q4 2755.464
#> 2017 Q1 2784.515
#> 2017 Q2 2794.781
#> 2017 Q3 2789.966
plot(IMPGSC1,grid.col = "white", col="blue")
